title: KICK-ASS 3  003 (2013) (c2c) (3 Covers) (Monafekk-Empire)
description:
Kick-Ass 3 #3

Story by Mark Millar
Art by John Romita Jr., Tom Palmer
Colors by Dean White, Michael Kelleher
Letters by Chris Eliopoulos
Cover by John Romita Jr., Tom Palmer, Dean White
Publisher: Marvel Icon
Release Date: September 11th, 2013

What's a tween girl assassin to do once she's locked up? Start running all the gangs in the joint, of course! After surviving the brutal pecking order of middle school, Hit-Girl finds jail just might be a little more up her alley. Meanwhile, Kick-Ass starts learning there's more to life than just superhero work.
